msgid ""
"KeePassRX is password manager for KeePass databases, designed for Ubuntu "
"Touch. It is licensed under the GNU AGPL v3 license."
msgstr ""
"El KeePassRX és un gestor de bases de dades KeePass, dissenyat per a "
"l'Ubuntu Touch. Està llicenciat sota una llicència GNU AGPL v3."

msgid ""
"The built-in KeePass icon images are licensed under a variety of licenses as "
"detailed in assets/COPYING."
msgstr ""
"Les imatges incorporades d'icones KeePass estan llicenciades sota una "
"varietat de llicències tal com es detalla a assets/COPYING."

